room_title: Escape room "Peek-a-Boo" by Live Game Escape in Salt Lake City

room_description: A local daycare had a series of mysterious disappearings and eerie ghost sightings. It is clear to your Spirit Removal Service that a clearing is in order. When you go in for the initial screening, the door shuts down behind you, and you are left with no choice but to face whatever is inside...
